      "title": "accused<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>\"被控犯罪的人\"，1590年代，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of accuse \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/accuse\">accuse</a>（动词）的过去分词。</p>"
